  m_Text: 'Muhammad Ubaid believes that children learn most effectively through play.
    Our mission is to create magical experiences that give kids the freedom to grow
    and thrive. We are dedicated to producing content that is as rich, engaging,
    and full of life as the young minds who enjoy it.


    Through our in-house
    studios and agile development process, we craft fun, captivating, and genuine
    content that kids love. We''re always evolving to deliver the high-quality experiences
    children have come to expect and enjoy.

'
